name: Warmup_Div05_Sub02
queryText:
SELECT DISTINCT
GmailD5S2.CPF,
GmailD5S2.NOME,
GmailD5S2.EMAIL,
GmailD5S2.EMAIL_VALIDO,
CASE

  WHEN CHARINDEX(' ', GmailD5S2.NOME) = 0 THEN GmailD5S2.NOME

  ELSE SUBSTRING( GmailD5S2.NOME , 1, CHARINDEX(' ', GmailD5S2.NOME) )

END AS PNOME
FROM Gmail_DIV05_SUB02 GmailD5S2
UNION
